parameters:
Young Luid: Mother! It's been a while! I have not neglected
my training and have gone to the battlefield to fulfill my
promise!

Queen Caron: Do not casually address me as 'Mother'. The one
standing before you is the Queen of the Fotizona Empire.

Young Luid: I apologize for my overwhelming emotions...
Please forgive my rudeness.

Queen Caron: Hehe, it is a mother's duty to teach etiquette.
I am glad to see that you have grown up so well. Mother is
pleased.
Young Luid: Your words of praise are greatly appreciated!

Queen Caron: Now, onto the main topic... From today onwards,
I want you to take on a different identity and inherit a
different family name.

Queen Caron: It is meaningless for someone of a middle-
class noble background like you to be involved in the task I
want to entrust to you.

Young Luid: Abandon my father's family name... Is that what
you are saying, Mother...?

Queen Caron: I want you, who will bear the empire on your
shoulders, to protect the prince who I am holding in my
arms.

Queen Caron: The new leader of the Imperial Shadow Division,
Ishekel... There is no one else but you who can fulfill such
an important role.

Young Luid: I just... wanted to meet you, even if it's just
for a moment, here...

Queen Caron: Luid, my beloved son... I truly want to hold
you like I did back then, and live together with you.

Queen Caron: However, the circumstances do not allow for
it... That is why I desperately want a connection with you.

Queen Caron: Why don't we try to reclaim the time we lost,
and increase the opportunities for us to meet...

There was no option to refuse Luid. The same beautiful face,
voice, hair, and eyes as that day...

Luid chose to continue being deceived by his mother, even if
her desires were tainted and her words were full of lies.
The sound of chains could be heard from somewhere,
unpleasantly ringing in his ears.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
